{"tid":862342,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"雞湯拉麵","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T09:35:01.000Z","uid":175988,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac86bf428c78691f477ebc701a57d4ec029b0c8","tid":862342,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:20:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>座銀 @ 上環</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RNSc96A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRNSc96A.jpg&h=b520d7bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>雞白湯拉麵</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麵質爽滑，掛湯能力唔錯<br />\n<br />\n雞湯底打至起泡，飲落綿滑濃郁，稍嫌過䶢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炸牛蒡幾特別，但一浸落湯就變到又腍又韌，質感同橡筋差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲肉片味道如同煙肉，肉味不足又有啲死䶢，完全無脂香<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論:唔會再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"eb1cf6cc788f288fbaeb275dabc16398a8990ccf","tid":862342,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:22:56.000Z","msg":"唔試沾麵？"},{"pid":"4fe542e46e89b8d230b1b61640196d13001a7259","tid":862342,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48112a6aa7da68f9c234da636c71cd6e27894b5","tid":862342,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好食喎"},{"pid":"accc38b4ba8431983ba2d086e905ab325dbb8383","tid":862342,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48112a6aa7da68f9c234da636c71cd6e27894b5","tid":862342,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c